{"about_the_game":"\u201cThe core, a compound found in all Slime, has always been something mystical and mysterious. The strange element could be synthesized by users, which allowed them to reason and manifest a unique power. Due to its inestimable value, an evil being began to extract it from the body of inhabitants of a Slime village, transforming its victims into slaves who had no capacity for logical reasoning and only followed the orders of their new master. While the remaining inhabitants of the village escaped, the terrible being commanded his new troops to hunt them down and remove their cores. This event marked the beginning of the conflict between the coreless Slimes and the Resistance, a group of people fleeing the attacks, known as the Slime Wars.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSlime Wars is a cooperative multiplayer game that combines elements of the Top Down Shooter and Party-Games genre. The game recreates an arena capable of supporting up to 4 players simultaneously, in which players must face enemies in frenetic combat.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCustomize your character the way you want and defend your territory against threats in Slime Wars.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Instructions -<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHold the Left Mouse Button to shoot;<br />\r\nUse the W, A, S, D keys to move the character;","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ready for Action!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2599360/2cd7af5495f27119c4762410a2ef5592f1b4eae0.jpg"},{"name":"Coreless's Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2599360/250b2ece2c958f2770b0746e0abe60cb14a80abf.jpg"},{"name":"Coreless's Destroyer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2599360/83a96eb734075cfc6e681a3fd957c7834bc99e00.jpg"},{"name":"Coreless's Nightmare","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2599360/ee06c4e3cab57364ce820845d0c67d7fef3ba560.jpg"}],"total":